{"title":"Far Insulinas","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Endocrinología/Far Insulinas-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Insulinas","guid":"XQXxdkHshtvjBB5_BsqHvQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Características\\NBioquímicas de la Insulina","guid":"M-yYAes_i7vYSWqgH90hMA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Estructura:","guid":"0MMWt3cxRhjyKdzx33P7Xg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Composición: Proteína de 51 aminoácidos.","guid":"Xl6JPfcfGvuZfuzgfCxxyA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"• Cadenas: Dos cadenas polipeptídicas\\N(A y B) unidas por puentes disulfuro.","guid":"WAFziUxZWkz6K4-EUV2GdA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Cadena A: 21 aminoácidos.","guid":"lRBoJ7gvbiw0RLVjtULb3Q","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Cadena B: 30 aminoácidos.","guid":"ydWf5tRYHsx3x2fUvjx0lQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"• Puentes Disulfuro: Dos entre cadenas (A7-B7, A20-B19)\\Ny uno intracadena en la cadena A (A6-A11).","guid":"F9yDaAnCCeSoc1dLp-5IKg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"2. Síntesis:","guid":"PRz17hUYdrv_89JqEni6fg","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Preproinsulina: Precursor inicial en el páncreas.","guid":"alkz75TORfAUZGxJosQ2Sw","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"• Proinsulina: Formada después de la escisión del péptido señal.","guid":"vxixBhqzyfZ8pWeIb3yfUA","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"• Insulina: Formada tras la escisión del péptido C de la proinsulina.","guid":"DWc-4kazWaB_icn1ALqyPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"3. Mecanismo\\Nde Acción:","guid":"aBzUfVbDEfwPnghu-nl6nA","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Receptor de Insulina: Receptor tirosina quinasa.","guid":"frd5D1C6gcZPkxKr12urRg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Unión de insulina al receptor → Autofosforilación del receptor.","guid":"2evGiFWg13JdxOUQR-RTjA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"• Activación de cascadas de señalización (PI3K/Akt, MAPK).","guid":"G7sKdBtjhrQRhCPrM-Fj8g","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"• Efectos\\NMetabólicos:","guid":"0MiEBSNfOPt7VvMoOQ7Wsw","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• ↑ Captación de glucosa (GLUT4 en músculo y tejido adiposo).","guid":"Un6VGkuorAZiT9FD2eJDPw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"• ↑ Glucogénesis.","guid":"7Tlp7WRJrFm09F47EfGZGg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"• ↑ Síntesis de lípidos y proteínas.","guid":"n2utEQcEG-WCtv8wJSHajg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"• ↓ Gluconeogénesis.","guid":"wGuBaL0ZjrNdq5uYv6IUQA","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"16","text":"• ↓ Glucogenólisis.","guid":"oPa481OEiHNfbU7NVLpuLg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"1","text":"4. Tipos de Insulina y\\NModificaciones Bioquímicas:","guid":"bi4D1N3eW2Z8T3XD8lliOQ","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Insulinas\\NHumanas:","guid":"DfJYYZpWygBysyfQvNPwLw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Regular (acción rápida).","guid":"adGgF6u-XBCNypQDRJasUw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• NPH (acción intermedia, adición de protamina).","guid":"1MQocCh4_ojMLBSGPzKuTA","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"• Análogos\\Nde Insulina:","guid":"DWR0IvPFsDiDeLDKepjFYg","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Modificaciones en la secuencia de aa de la insulina por bioingeniería ➜ alteran farmacocinética.","guid":"oyO11cFZv0Yvm3b-s1ZTHg","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Uso combinado de análogos rápidos + análogos sostenidos ➜ simular secreción fisiológica de célula beta (26).","guid":"dBi2lmFeS70ikHIXL1VhcQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Ultrarrápidas: Lispro,\\NAspártica, Glulisina.","guid":"h21HWn2Atj6gP6gak3NJag","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Insulina lispro: cambio en residuos 28 y 29 de la cadena B (20).","guid":"T-2EUDQAjqcgtUxfIAcQfw","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• Insulina aspart: cambio en residuo 28 (21).","guid":"yXZa0shcayGL8Tm4FJlV7g","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"• Insulina glulisina: sustitución de asparagina por lisina en B3 y lisina por ácido glutámico en B29 (22).","guid":"6UYNJrktvDmVTlLSUERzBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"26","text":"• Lentas: Glargina, Detemir.","guid":"QjZISU4bXhnSerHpOge6TA","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Insulina\\Nglargina:","guid":"6_qWRHGlyIGZtxWVbroDzg","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Residuo glicina en A21 + adición de dos argininas en B31 y B32 ➜ carga + y solubilidad en pH ácido (23).","guid":"iHmUjdT5aQS-WGERJXJqpw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• pH neutro (tejido SC) ➜ precipitación y absorción lenta ➜ acción sostenida.","guid":"MOBO9gKpwdg_tBAB74OrkQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"• No mezclar con otras insulinas (23).","guid":"iSHtNwaPu73gT57pVv_VoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"• Insulina\\Ndetemir:","guid":"FieiK6ggMLbqZk5ksNpjWw","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Ácido mirístico (C14) unido a lisina en B29 + extracción de treonina en B30 (24).","guid":"lmRNwSCQwEXbwPMgKsT90g","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Soluble en pH neutro ➜ permanece en estado líquido post-inyección SC.","guid":"eznhSZawnNvjXnOru0fCIw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"• Acción sostenida por asociación molecular y unión reversible a albúmina (24).","guid":"Tf8fVSbXJlDtj4hGiYXzeQ","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"38","text":"• Menor variabilidad intrasujeto comparada con glargina o NPH (25).","guid":"BkX8bg7tpUHBKlBOkHW-tw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"26","text":"• Ultralentas: Degludec.","guid":"xbB6UDzReBS7wnKKeUuLIA","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"• Detemir: Adición de ácido mirístico para prolongar acción a través de u