o de glicemia en tiempo real.","guid":"kIyPTB7Skx1cI3mOhiWZkg","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Potencial para desplazar a glucómetros cubiertos por AUGE en el futuro.","guid":"wH0HfEyVXeh3izRIV0CCjw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"0","text":"Farmacocinética de\\Npreparaciones de insulina","guid":"nexe-EVEEx77wpGjDGntXg","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"A. Insulina\\NPrandial:","guid":"wicQvk8TJGGFA3bcQnUBlA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"1. Lispro, Lispro-aabc, Aspart,\\NFaster Aspart, Glulisina:","guid":"KW925Aw2gcdtBeTbhWBrxQ","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"• Inicio acción: 15-30 min","guid":"Vv7ehrGxDie1t7sr9Xf09w","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"• Pico efectivo: 1-3 h","guid":"EJ01eJ6xm-4GAuXLUjKWXw","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"130","text":"• Duración: 4-6 h","guid":"Hu545vJfw5O_YZaXgNoPSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"129","text":"2. Regular:","guid":"cRqgqj80-11VlclqH3223A","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• Inicio acción: 30 min","guid":"bC4_cHyxHlyiKqtvdoFl-w","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"• Pico efectivo: 1.5-3.5 h","guid":"iEDoCdIT01mYoWgLbU0a5A","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"• Duración: 8 h","guid":"Wv6nhgcbDDOHNfa29MPpJg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"128","text":"B. Insulina\\NBasal:","guid":"QkicQMDuhd8GUPFB6E8oqg","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"1. NPH:","guid":"eMVsdfURk-HGiBHv-U_JyA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Vida media: 4.4 h","guid":"8yuRud9uk3WZPRNg-nQv2A","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"• Pico efectivo: 4-6 h","guid":"k6T2JYRyCMUftM52uVoAtw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"• Duración: 12 h","guid":"l5zNfC-Ja6OkPTHak9K2VQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"138","text":"2. Glargina:","guid":"Rtix9npIqhczaZFmtywsQw","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• U-100:","guid":"kRR8Umfobya0CAhZzYFa3w","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Vida media: 12 h","guid":"C-RBfqI0YtX7cIJF-i2xIA","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"• Pico efectivo: No pronunciado","guid":"MR9sZzYx_S3dTNFFPMCOMw","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"• Duración: 20-24 h","guid":"3gZzD6qgSKitYd5_6kE4Cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"• U-300:","guid":"N7Lnba0XiCeSdI_PH2GOmw","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"• Vida media: 19 h","guid":"SZuffznw-x6zOWJJsJijbg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"• Pico efectivo: No pronunciado","guid":"ZWLwROrPAsUqYIcf7lV5vQ","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"• Duración: 20-24 h","guid":"5iVRgw-FwVpAOxp7BRMNhQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"138","text":"3. Detemir:","guid":"AD-PcJiojSx-nppJg7V0nw","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"• Vida media: 5-7 h","guid":"-EzPj0aGanWAnCtnRBledA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"• Pico efectivo: 3-9 h","guid":"AMgTFM5db-EPZsDRvcyBzQ","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"• Duración: 6-24 h","guid":"zO3SxrcjaDyGKgm7GZA2IQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"138","text":"4. Degludec\\N(U-100, U-200):","guid":"Q_qeop0GUNf-8QCu9iDrxg","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• Vida media: 25 h","guid":"K6ztSIHm-D2XRQgs2Gw87Q","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Pico efectivo: No pronunciado","guid":"EbeT2Nzr6KSYdNo1x8BBpA","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"• Duración: >24 h","guid":"9XEgkrAQ15WiF9X4hc0q6w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"160","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGenerales","guid":"KjTKAvI5EGAOUjn97eWjiA","children":[{"id":"161","parent":"160","text":"• Insulina: Fármaco hipoglicemiante más potente, sin contraindicaciones ni dosis máxima.","guid":"OgW--LGxwWIg4sdZTticUg","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"160","text":"Evaluación\\NPrevia","guid":"gbIa9g6QdNlRz7MGqQHdxQ","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• Factores a considerar: Motivación del paciente, nivel de hiperglicemia, complicaciones crónicas, fragilidad, expectativa de vida, riesgo de hipoglicemia.","guid":"NwwVV-5uFM4cfV0O8usoEA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"• Condiciones\\Nespeciales:","guid":"5t1U0NpIX_52fJhW7tIQcA","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"• Nefropatía crónica, daño hepático, enfermedades terminales, hemodiálisis → ↓ requerimiento insulínico.","guid":"vlBU4AYG4Gqc4DQRXtBing","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"• Tratamientos esteroidales → ↑ requerimiento insulínico.","guid":"2MTpASxAZapMFxzftNMBYA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"160","text":"Efectos\\NAdversos","guid":"UCO_p-ZaDjbL0vZZNRWAeA","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Inicio:","guid":"ni1Nsn6hBoa_BkCJ3jTXsg","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"• Edema transitorio.","guid":"NQqv9TTSHGPVjl7kdd_i8g","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"• Presbiopenia (trastorno transitorio de refracción).","guid":"Hmk7ORJn6j6VjNg6j4xAqA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"168","text":"• Intensificación transitoria de dolores polineuropáticos.","guid":"lXpYfLQySB186d90m0u9JA","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"168","text":"• Alergias (baja frecuencia).","guid":"fvPX9F8Xwl3fv8Bi4KYOfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"167","text":"• Mediano/largo\\Nplazo:","guid":"5TLd5aj-XuMkdKwZflvNjA","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"• Lipodistrofias en sitio de inyección.","guid":"_bk2A1cBbQSeFl4KemCSNA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"• Aumento de peso (131).","guid":"RgrbqO0h9UTihnYSdoIpUA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"Insulinoterapia en DMT1","guid":"cLo0Q2_Eho8Y1rXgl67h3g","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"1. Metas:","guid":"H1mpeXDplSSDrpIl1J75mA","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"• HbA1c < 7%","guid":"hC2UpPphVkLkfS3-Iwv24w","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"• Glicemia: 70-180 mg/dl","guid":"N0Yg0S3BF7Dj5krhTsrKnw","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"• Rango deseado: 140-160 mg/dl","guid":"hRy0UntPv_SOCK5immraUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"176","text":"2. Esquema ideal:\\NBasal-Bolo","guid":"W6PNzf_ZFkZbFcSHkEyuqA","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• Insulina Basal: Larga acción (1 vez/día)","guid":"7j43Mkyrk_7BPC4sgZfDYw","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"• Bolos Prandiales: Según CHO ingeridos, niveles de glicemia, actividad física esperada","guid":"wliP2IH5ZycPVL0otyNEng","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"176","text":"3. Bomba de\\NInsulina:","guid":"LEoRSBazK2Y_pZSSrCeMIg","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• Ventajas:","guid":"fnVi5Ut4KQnE77UgPPs1ng","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"• ↓ Riesgo de hipoglicemias","guid":"lvexF0RxlGmniWFbwA916w","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"• Conveniencia","guid":"OpLZCmWAHpILXFDQ83RBqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"184","text":"• Desventajas:","guid":"bofyQKni3sa8_UGfPyInoQ","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"• ↑ Riesgo de CAD si se bloquea o falla","guid":"JmQXaaMJTDe5Yzq5asq6Yw","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"• Costosa","guid":"zE_hRlpmZLenerhtqgmoDQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"• Requiere capacidad cognitiva para operar","guid":"gJxPbbLIJeNt_NhAaqOx0w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"176","text":"4. Dosis Total\\Nde Insulina:","guid":"tzbJfRhg1JUzPgHnr8J-Dg","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"• Inicial: 0.2-0.5 UI/kg/día","guid":"JSq2JcmXxXIdit08Pl1OOg","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"• Aumenta: 0. 6-0.7 UI/kg/día","guid":"-svjz7se2tWIOe4ERKH9kA","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"• ↑ Dosis en adolescentes y situaciones de estrés","guid":"xMYAgkv_kvgaslHZGxRkwQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"176","text":"5. Composición:","guid":"3-imxZmJE68_9AOCOxbaKQ","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• 40-50%: Insulina Basal (Degludec o Glargina U-300, 1 vez/día;\\NGlargina U-100 o Detemir, 1-2 veces/día)","guid":"svgfnp2jieZ5fg5OItXHNw","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"• Resto: Insulina Rápida (Con comidas)","guid":"qxww7KzhfOo-K1oeK2eI8A","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"• Insulina lenta: Cualquier momento del día, usualmente mañana o noche","guid":"ieKZlO8Hxi0lHXYc7vMCXQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"176","text":"Ratio y Sensibilidades\\Nen Insulinoterapia","guid":"V8rt0h7iK0rZazD6uPbykA","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"1. Ratio\\Nde CHO:","guid":"2EOTkzXntwZ0I8F3KAiQJg","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• Fórmula: 450 ÷ Dosis diaria de insulina (DDI)","guid":"X_St_RO6hLnbeh5F_1i7Dg","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"• Ejemplo: DDI = 45 UI → Ratio = 450/45 = 10","guid":"FTy26UFaZilsdLy-2H41ew","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"201","text":"• Interpretación: 1 UI de insulina neutraliza 10 g de CHO","guid":"cfqsWxFgpAooWHA6Oei-kw","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"200","text":"2. Sensibilidad:","guid":"T5azDan2rybh1qdqE6CHEQ","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"• Fórmula: 1500 ÷ Dosis diaria de insulina (DDI)","guid":"s91X1Ety7q7zHUoo-SK7EQ","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"• Ejemplo: DDI = 45 UI → Sensibilidad = 1500/45 = 33 (aprox.)","guid":"qex6o_0V7MJ4g7W4SziLog","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"205","text":"• Interpretación: 1 UI de insulina ↓ glicemia en 33 mg/dl","guid":"jRi39IEzRpHme2p8ApLEbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"200","text":"3. Cálculo de\\NDosis Prandial:","guid":"QgFJjKerz9zmFeHQd31qPA","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"• Considerar CHO ingeridos","guid":"7fpe8t6OldcHtxX6mxtJoA","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"• Dosis por CHO: CHO ingeridos ÷ Ratio","guid":"kaXZlqedRujbehtWGo6d1Q","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"209","text":"• Corrección según sensibilidad:","guid":"zq5mZaQHFTqN1jTLm7jV6w","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• Glicemia objetivo: 120-140 mg/dl","guid":"y0BvE3TM6NxF_U0adhuW3A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"214","parent":"200","text":"• Ejemplo:","guid":"4cKERZLhDw1ODllQBJ8dfQ","children":[{"id":"215","parent":"214","text":"• 1 marraqueta = 60 g CHO","guid":"7w8Pbd6m6Mn0__9OJmhLPA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"214","text":"• Ratio = 10 → 60/10 = 6 UI","guid":"Hoe00QApFZZGO5RiZ1k96Q","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"214","text":"• Glicemia pre-prandial = 190 mg/dl","guid":"fZQgVAazyos-lZjfYtJquQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"218","parent":"200","text":"• Corrección:","guid":"_1ArJvnmiXeHVXxXDhv_bQ","children":[{"id":"219","parent":"218","text":"• 120-150 mg/dl = +1 UI","guid":"yK-hRYk6PbOz6IFegjvx-A","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"218","text":"• 150-180 mg/dl = +2 UI","guid":"OapcV1AvyEdGC8BTK0xJrw","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"218","text":"• 180-210 mg/dl = +3 UI","guid":"I0BS08IDDo8OhO5lmOBUaA","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"218","text":"• Total insulina: 6 UI (CHO) + 3 UI (Corrección) = 9 UI","guid":"KUn0kCVd-q-qSEJ5m4btZg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"0","text":"Diabetes Tipo 2","guid":"Y6Wy2gcFadKwZspusBE8Og","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"1. Indicación de\\NInsulinoterapia","guid":"R4158YsUV6Zg5Fh_dUWV1Q","children":[{"id":"225","parent":"224","text":"Primera Línea","guid":"MaOigv90ZryUhx-MwsHmfw","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"• DM sintomática:","guid":"G4oAP_NS5B2JIZi30UbiMQ","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"• Poliuria","guid":"ZSWpH3RNDJnIhsYV7jXtTQ","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"• Polidipsia","guid":"xfrQwxUWRYDr02cYJT_gYw","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"226","text":"• Pérdida de peso","guid":"8tJ-7XWNXb7hylV_O11KSA","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"226","text":"• Glicemias > 300 mg/dl","guid":"3PqO0jI6Hj9FL9lWZ8qJ_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"225","text":"• HbA1c > 9%","guid":"gZNBuplqXNKD-J82NVwh3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"232","parent":"224","text":"Cuando no se logran metas glicémicas individualizadas,\\Noptimizando antidiabéticos orales, idealmente con arGLP-1.","guid":"IJULQQQh1tdKc_vHe2X-7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"223","text":"2. Alternativas:","guid":"oH-IZ2e4TGx2G7JFEfLftQ","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"• Agonistas de GLP-1","guid":"AsBYZb-6Ho-tXMdMU2VSBQ","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"• No hay estudios comparativos explícitos con insulina en diabetes descompensada","guid":"X4sQLHRSuSqk9dkhZ5a6yg","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"• Se prefiere insulina por falta de datos comparativos","guid":"ydKtERP8zEoMiIzuhoDuIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"223","text":"3. Insulina Inicial:","guid":"y_hLAJye3rnFVee8PS5PGQ","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"• Insulina basal: Control de hiperglicemia post absortiva, reducción de gluconeogénesis hepática.","guid":"w2699F7LU4DdEqUgf41PDQ","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"237","text":"• Insulinas de\\Nlarga acción:","guid":"eqVo1wdXUsRRrDYqmz6WbA","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"• NPH","guid":"j4QxJXKsoTRwW5mjStvcxw","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"239","text":"• Glargina","guid":"eIVpKrCIRWQ3AxHXuHwYBg","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"239","text":"• Detemir","guid":"Ux7oslYJUlmjIl3Gc0DBeQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"239","text":"• Degludec","guid":"FKUwejEGYswycSRffPumLA","children":[]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"237","text":"• Dosis nocturna","guid":"UfYAoQszVk_SpM43G8u3FQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"245","parent":"223","text":"3. Esquema\\NBasal-Bolo","guid":"gQLAKtow63GKha_DcxQySw","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"• Indicaciones: A1c > meta individualizada con antidiabéticos y insulina basal.","guid":"WwP8jVSxJDk3yrrAo4KYjw","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"245","text":"• Insulina rápida/análogos\\Nrápidos y ultra-rápidos:","guid":"PZ9OeCadHptW4q0ymtDXlQ","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"• Administración: 10-20 min previo a comidas.","guid":"yBMVF_7IMHcDIQschc0qcg","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"247","text":"• Dosis: Fijas o basadas en glicemia capilar y carga glicémica de la comida.","guid":"hkR-dokklVD8o9juVtl5_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"250","parent":"245","text":"• Complejidad: Alto riesgo de hipoglicemias, manejo y evaluación por especialista (130).","guid":"NVAEqmhvZf8ynLpY_wI5rA","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"245","text":"Ajuste de Dosis","guid":"GW6AOQIl2JitqUOGwSMafA","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"• Frecuencia: Precoz y continuo, basado en glucometría capilar o MCG (129).","guid":"Q-ywAiRAPYq5yYF55Mt9FA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"223","text":"Esquema de Insulina y\\NHorario de Automonitoreo","guid":"_n3dRJxp2mAOKxucjx23Zg","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"1. Insulina Neutral Protamine Hagedorn (NPH),\\Ndetemir o glargina U100 al acostarse","guid":"6rKoV2Kyrwe1HeYkpWKHOw","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"• Horario: A primera hora de la mañana antes\\Nde ingerir la primera comida del día.","guid":"apCmG-pjClQaaQ-GqUXZDA","children":[]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"253","text":"2. Insulina NPH o\\Ndetemir doble dosis","guid":"CfndWNP2RDTQslnsuN3iQw","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"• A primera hora de la mañana antes de ingerir la primera comida del día.","guid":"Z29RQfTPKdFlTu6QbLy5yg","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"256","text":"• A media tarde entre 6 a 8 horas después de aplicar la dosis matinal.","guid":"NIFibROgCI97vixcghf1fA","children":[]}]},{"id":"259","parent":"253","text":"3. Insulina glargina U100 matinal,\\Ninsulina glargina U300 o degludec","guid":"kIow22IzZ1A-ISccFGBRvg","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"• Nota: Recordar que tarda tres días en alcanzar estabilidad.","guid":"hDm04OTWMBk8x1rtTjDWwA","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"• A primera hora de la mañana antes de ingerir la primera comida del día.","guid":"f4Ig-UGrRizAGcos-A5KgA","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"259","text":"• En el vespertino antes de ingerir la última comida del día.","guid":"5kCC7Ls2704JfLhMj43VqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"263","parent":"253","text":"4. Insulina\\Nbasal - bolo","guid":"8U3UhveIvEINmx_CvYcWgQ","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"• A primera hora de la mañana antes de ingerir la primera comida del día.","guid":"gsj0sLACakpvgCt6mXhu4g","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"• Antes de cada ingesta de comida.","guid":"jI9blHL9-wEWq3ybzO0CMQ","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"• 2 horas post ingesta según indicación médica.","guid":"DbmxEWXl9gcz43KqZjuNIQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"223","text":"Insulinas\\NPremezcladas","guid":"ZkRy46-VdxOxvY_rHjJiLg","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"Definición","guid":"ImOQ0FsnORIHy_xn_BCrYg","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Composición: Mezcla de insulina de acción regular o rápida con insulina protaminizada (acción lenta).","guid":"x27RfCajSryR3Hj1dPG4Mg","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"• Concentración basal: 75-80%.","guid":"4aUjuy6t_8qYD6eWs4hCMg","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"268","text":"• Resto: Insulina análoga rápida o prandial.","guid":"U8nZNJvq7bO6sJJIwYObbg","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"268","text":"• Administración: Jeringas o lápices graduados.","guid":"FmdGRJpqDWQG03M6UQ5TNg","children":[]}]},{"id":"273","parent":"267","text":"Uso y Eficacia","guid":"dsCc8mL6-gR30YUIDSWRjQ","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"• Alternativa para intensificación de terapia: Simplicidad en dosificación y costo comparativo (97).","guid":"-q0NwrmC5WEIeYKT0N4M6g","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"273","text":"• Comparación:","guid":"4n_kzYqJf_o1VEnujERxAg","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"• Versus insulinas basales con antidiabéticos: No mejora control glicémico, mayor riesgo de hipoglicemias (132).","guid":"cbD-ozZRvYcQ84RRc4xCsg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"• Versus esquema basal-bolo: No mejora control glicémico, mayor riesgo de hipoglicemias (133).","guid":"Sxr-i5_b4v3m32k1AP3SOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"278","parent":"273","text":"• Recomendación: No recomendadas salvo condiciones especiales según criterio médico.","guid":"d1kEsLNzCFMTUsvS-Vdn2w","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":278,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Endocrinología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Endocrinología","filename":"Far Insulinas-2024","id":"map_574","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Far Insulinas-2024"}